{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_51_01",
  "title": "川咲さくら",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふんふーん。いつも私のそ～ば～に～\nギョギョっと、ギョギョっと！",
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5666668574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、さくら。何かいいことでもあった？\n{user}さんと打ち合わせだったのよね？",
      "startTime": 14.2000001907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7999999364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、聞いて聞いて！　私にも『ミラクル☆\nアイドルバースデー！』のお話が来たの！",
      "startTime": 21.3666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.4333332698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルのやってみたいことを叶えてくれる\n雑誌のお誕生日企画よね。その打ち合わせだったんだ",
      "startTime": 27.0333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.7999999364
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　今から撮影当日が楽しみだよ～。……そうだ！\n良ければ琴乃ちゃん、私の企画に参加してくれない？",
      "startTime": 39.3333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.500001971
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私が？　うん、分かった。私の時は、さくらに参加して\nもらったし。ちなみに、何をお願いするつもりなの？",
      "startTime": 50.100001971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.3666686376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それはね～、えへへ～。なんと、なんと……！\nえへへへ～～",
      "startTime": 64.5666686376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.4666630428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ、さくら、にやけてないで教えて？",
      "startTime": 67.4666630428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2666630428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、嬉し過ぎて、つい\nえっとね、それはなんと……これから決めます！！",
      "startTime": 76.5333297094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.5333297094
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1333297094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まだ決まってなかったんだ……\n自信満々だから、もう決まってるのかと思っちゃった",
      "startTime": 87.2333297094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.7333297094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや琴乃ちゃん、まだ決まってないっていうことは\n無限の可能性があるってことだよ！",
      "startTime": 96.1333297094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.4666630428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ひ～！　早くこの真っ白なアンケート用紙に\n書き込みたい！　どのペンで書こうかな～",
      "startTime": 104.0333297094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1333271663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "もし悩んだら、いつでも相談に乗るから\n……って言っても、この感じなら大丈夫だと思うけど",
      "startTime": 112.5333271663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0333271663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう！　じゃあ、ギョギョッと書いて\nシュビビッて{user}さんに出してくるね",
      "startTime": 120.7333271663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一週間後",
      "startTime": 125.0666604996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 126.0999984106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "このお菓子、誰のだろう……。イチゴ味、美味しそう\nうぅ……後で買ってくるから、一つだけ……",
      "startTime": 137.9666650773,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000.0015894,
          "startTime": 144.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "ごどのぢゃあああああん！！",
      "startTime": 144.7999892553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "うわあっ！？　ご、ごめんっ、さくらのだった！？\nま、まだ食べてないから……！",
      "startTime": 151.766655922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃなくて……。お誕生日企画のことなんだけど\nぜんっっっっっっぜん決まらないの！　どうしよう！？",
      "startTime": 160.9333134334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ええぇ！？",
      "startTime": 166.6666498184,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3233.346112499987,
          "startTime": 169.8999959309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、さくら。寮にあったお菓子、一杯持ってきたから\n糖分補給しながら、二人で考えよう？",
      "startTime": 177.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……。あの後、一杯アンケート書いて\n出したんだけど、数が多過ぎるって言われちゃって",
      "startTime": 186.2333286923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "当日にやりたいことよね、いくつ書いたの？",
      "startTime": 191.0666599911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "千個……",
      "startTime": 195.6333266577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "多過ぎでしょっっ！？\n愛の腹筋の回数じゃないんだから",
      "startTime": 199.2666599911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "正確には、千と二百十五個だったかな……？\nそこから減らしたんだけど、まだ多いみたい……",
      "startTime": 207.9666589738,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.333333299981,
          "startTime": 212.6999923071
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと読ませてもらうわね\n真っ白だったアンケート用紙が、真っ黒になってる……",
      "startTime": 217.8666589738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "えっと『星見市民全員で魚魚っとさん音頭を踊りたい』\n『星見プロで宇宙旅行に行きたい』……",
      "startTime": 232.0333256405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "規模が大きい……\nというか、星見市民全員で踊るって……？",
      "startTime": 240.7999923071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "そのままの意味だよ？　その日は二十四時間\n市内に魚魚っとさん音頭が鳴り響くの",
      "startTime": 249.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11433.332316100006,
          "startTime": 260.6333323161
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "二十四時間やるんだ……\nとりあえず、叶えるのが大変そうなのは消して、っと",
      "startTime": 257.1666630429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "がーん！　うぅ、でも自分じゃ三百個までしか減らせ\nなかったし……お願いします、琴乃先生……！",
      "startTime": 271.2666589739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "先生ではないんだけど……。『魚魚っとさんの抱き\nまくらを発売してほしい』……これはいけそうかな？",
      "startTime": 281.1666589739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "やった！　もし新しく魚魚っとさんのグッズが出るん\nだったら、一番ほしかったんだ。寝る時も一緒だよ～",
      "startTime": 290.8999923072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。えっと、あとは……この端っこに書いてある\n『家族でパーティーがしたい』、っていうのは？",
      "startTime": 306.1333256406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "あ……それは、毎年やってることなの。入院中も\n私のお誕生日には、どんなに忙しくても来てくれてね",
      "startTime": 316.1999923072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "最近、お仕事が忙しくて、家族で過ごす時間も少なく\nなってたから、ちょうどいいかなって",
      "startTime": 326.0333256406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、両親からは、「せっかくのお話だから、さくらが\nやりたいことをお願いしたら？」って、今回言われてて",
      "startTime": 334.7666589739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "実際、雑誌の企画で、ホームパーティーの様子を\n撮影するのって、ちょっと地味だよね",
      "startTime": 343.3666589739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、さくら\n本当は、これが一番やりたいことなんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 350.1999923072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "startTime": 355.6333256406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "さくらがやりたいことなら、それをやろう？\nどう盛り上げるかは、編集部の人も考えてくれると思う",
      "startTime": 361.6999923072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私も一緒に考えるから\n家族は大事にしないと",
      "startTime": 369.9333256406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr022.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……\nうん、ありがとう。えへへ、じゃあこれにする",
      "startTime": 374.6666569394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-skr023.m4a",
      "text": "他のは、後で消しゴムで消さないとだね。あむ……\nあ、このお菓子美味しい。はい、琴乃ちゃん、あーん",
      "startTime": 386.2999902727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_01-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "じ、自分で食べれるから\n……でも、元気になったみたいで良かった",
      "startTime": 398.1999902727,
      "sfxList": [
